{
  "texts": [
    "Such information is valuable to guide future developments of Optical Chemical Structure Recognition models.",
    "Benchmarks and metrics.",
    "Here, we characterize benchmarks and metrics used in the evaluation of the ingestion pipeline and the database.",
    "Two benchmark datasets are introduced: D2C-RND (Document to Chemical structures, Random) and D2C-UNI (Document to Chemical structures, Uniform).",
    "D2C-RND contains 325 pages, 378 images, and 200 molecules, following a random distribution of chemical images."
  ]
}